8:
We're on the surface! We made it
back to Palpebra!
26:
I am relieved to see you are safe. We
must hurry, Stella is waiting for you
to bring the lance!
34:
Alk... Do you remember the
shopkeeper who worked here? I
wonder if he made it out safely...
37:
I... still remember that beaming grin
on his face when I told him how
delicious his food was.
51:
It's okay. You are my hero, Alk. You
must go and fulfill your duty.
55:
Even now, I sense it. Your Oudo
resonates with anger. With sorrow.
These emotions are now mine as
well—and that is why I shall fight.
58:
I will give it my all, till I am spent—I
will fight on your behalf, in your
place.
70:
We must form a safe route for
evacuation. If we can save even one
more soul, it will have been worth it.
74:
The enemy is strengthening their
position in sector 13?
77:
You, report on the Guild Knights'
situation! What of the platoon
stationed in sector 13?
80:
Er... That's the thing—there IS no
platoon assigned there.
82:
That area is beyond the city wall!
The top brass said we don't have the
budget to be defending slums.
85:
Beyond the wall? I fear we may not
make it in time...
89:
The three of you, follow me!
Everyone else, execute the plan
precisely as we discussed! Go!
95:
Over here, everyone—a tactical
retreat into the Kaleidoscope and
everything will be okay! The Guild
Knights will keep us safe!
99:
Yep. You hear that kids? Be good
and listen to Miss Lilie.
105:
...Still, isn't this too little too late? No
way we're going to make it on time,
and without backup... What a mess.
120:
The hell?! Did you not hear me, you
stupid hunk of junk?!
132: Tear it to pieces, my dragonlings!
141:
Talk about a one-trick pony. Is That
the only thing you know how to say?
"Don't move?" Use your damn head
for once.
151:
This is bad! We don't have time to
be fighting like this—we need to RUN!
156: In that case, use your power on me.
161:
Use your words to bind me! Order
me not to run away, no matter what!
Do it NOW!
172:
I can't stop shaking. My body's in
full-on flight mode... So hurry up and
order me to fight. Then you can
make your escape.
181: Lilie, take this boy to safety. Please.
186:
But what about you? You can't
mean to stay here?
192:
No time for chatter! Hightail it out of
here, unless you want that boy to
die! This is your job, isn't it? Then do
it!
208:
"You and I can win this fight!" There.
Those are my words. Now you have
to believe them.
218:
Fine, so be it. Just make sure not to
get in my way.
223:
God, you're such a prick, you know
that?!
241:
We are here to help! If you require
aid, please raise your voices!
245:
Doesn't look like there's anyone
here... Inaho, let's move on to the
next sector.
